                    <span>I must agree with the other reviews of this book -- it is a captivating read.  The only reason it took me two days to finish this book is that I do have a job and family that need a good portion of my time.  
<br />
<br />This book was very well written and provides an inside look at the founding of a business where the needs of the customer truly is what it values the most.  In fact, this book should be a must read for anyone thinking of starting their own business regardless of the industry.  </span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Surprisingly great read!</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
